genphy_update_link \- update link status in \fIphydev\fR
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'int\ genphy_update_link('u
.BI "int genphy_update_link(struct\ phy_device\ *\ " "phydev" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIphydev\fR
.RS 4
target phy_device struct
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Update the value in phydev\->link to reflect the current link value\&. In order to do this, we need to read the status register twice, keeping the second value\&.
